<para style="p">A psalm of Solomon.</para>

<para style="b" />

<para style="q1">

<verse number="1" style="v" />Give the king your righteous decrees, God,</para>

<para style="q1">your righteousness to the king's son.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="2" style="v" />May he judge your people with righteousness</para>

<para style="q1">and your poor with justice.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="3" style="v" />May the mountains produce peace for the people;</para>

<para style="q1">may the hills produce righteousness.</para>
